imdb.title: Glitter Girls Club
plot: Young, fun, often-goofy host - Jaidyn-Bleau (aka "Bleau) - takes viewers on a weekly adventure of guided, kid/family-friendly DIY projects that include crafts, activities, recipes, science projects, games, contests and more.
